  "body": "### Component\n\nForge\n\n### Describe the feature you would like\n\nAs raised here https://github.com/foundry-rs/foundry/issues/1709 it'd be useful to suppress all output so the output can be piped to other commands\r\n\r\n\r\nwe already can suppress solc related output via:\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/foundry-rs/foundry/blob/0e258fb191ad32db70a8a461763053990dc88789/cli/src/compile.rs#L208\r\n\r\n\r\nso if we introduce another flag, `silent: bool` in \r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/foundry-rs/foundry/blob/0e258fb191ad32db70a8a461763053990dc88789/cli/src/cmd/forge/build.rs#L65\r\n\r\nthen we can use that instead\n\n### Additional context\n\n_No response_",
